              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Breakup yields for the 9Be1208Pb system, which largely",
                "result from the 8Be(g.s.)+n channel, have been",
                "extracted from data taken in the measurement described",
                "in A0712 Entry."
              ]
            }
          ],
