                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "To provide an absolute normalization for the scattering",
                "yield, two monitor detectors were used. These were",
                "silicon surface barrier detectors, positioned at ~15",
                "degree to the beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "An array of telescopes using position sensitive silicon",
                "detectors enabled reaction products to be identified",
                "and their energy and scattering angle to be recorded",
                " (to improve the angular resolution, masks with ten",
                "slots were placed in front of the telescopes)."
              ]
            }
          ],
